INTERLAKE STEAMSHIP COMPANY, Appellant, v. CITY OF TOLEDO, Appellee. No. 7184. Circuit Court of Appeals, Sixth Circuit. April 9, 1937. McKeehan, Merrick, Arter & Stewart, of Cleveland, Ohio, for appellant. Martin S. Dodd, of Toledo, Ohio, for appellee.

Before HICKS, MACK, and ALLEN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The decree below is affirmed for the reasons given in the memorandum opinion of the District Judge dated May 9, 1935.
